I frequently pull up a filter for work, and examine each issue, closing them, then editing the next item.  It would be really helpful if the resolve issue screen had a Close and Next button as well as a Resolve and Next button so the user can close and issue and move to the next item in the filter.  Right now you have to click Close, then click Next to move on.

Ideally, it would only appear if you have a filter active.

