Could be related to JRA-1558, but currently when I Move an issue (let's say from a Support Request to a Bug or Enhancement), it does not link the old issue to the new.  When I attempt to view the originally created issue, it just tells me that it does not exist, and I have to search for the new issue in Bugs or Enhancements Project.  Keeping a log or trail of where the issue has gone would be helpful for us, as well as our clients who have created the issue.

